snippet.textDisplay: This is the plot in a nutshell. The Jellicle Cats are some sort of cat religion. They hold an annual singing contest (judged by Old Deuteronomy) to determine who will be sent to the Heaviside Layer and be reincarnated. Macavity kidnaps the other contestants so he will win by default. When that fails, he kidnaps and threatens to kill Old Deuteronomy. Mister Mistoffelees uses his magic to get Macavity back. Old Deuteronomy chooses Grizabella, who ends up riding her way to the Heaviside Layer.
